WEBVTT

32:06.630 --> 32:09.240 line:80%
♪ It seems to be the fire of love ♪

32:08.070 --> 32:09.400 line:80%
Later, my parents died.

32:09.860 --> 32:11.600 line:80%
♪ Just a few sparks ♪

32:10.720 --> 32:11.900 line:80%
To make a living,

32:12.050 --> 32:16.930 line:80%
♪ Let me hide in your heart ♪

32:12.550 --> 32:15.010 line:80%
I had no choice
but to start butchering pigs.

32:15.220 --> 32:17.960 line:80%
I even used a stick
to teach people a lesson a few times.
